---
import '../../styles/global.css';
import '@fontsource-variable/azeret-mono'
import MainLayout from '../../Layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title='Gareth Gillespie | Muscle Rage' description="Graphic Design, Website Design and 3D modelling for Muscle Rage">
		<main class="portfolio-main">
			<h1 class="smaller-h1">Muscle Rage</h1>
			<div class="info">
				<p>Muscle Rage is a supplement brand specialising in supplements specifically for muscle building, and male health.</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<section class="tools">
			<p>Tools:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Adobe CC</li>
				<li>WordPress</li>
				<li>Affinity</li>
				<li>Brevo</li>
				<li>Blender</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
		<section class="port-top">
			<div class="port-img-1">
				<img src="/muscle-rage-brand-guidelines.webp" />
			</div>
			<div class="port-info-1">
				<h4>
					Branding
				</h4>
				<ul>
					<li>Undertook customer research, using first hand data from GA4, WooCommerce and Social Channels</li>
					<li>Setup clear brand guidelines and ideal customer personas</li>
					<li>Took the packaging design in a different direction, in line with brand guidelines and the needs of management</li>
					<li>Brought all product packaging in line with new label sizes, and sourced a new print provider for future product runs</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section class="port-grid">
			<div>
				<h4>
					Marketing
				</h4>
				<ul>
					<li>Enable automated email flows (Welcome new customers, recover abandoned carts, win back series)</li>
					<li>Brought consistency to email design, based on brand guidelines</li>
					<li>Segmented audiences based on ideal personas</li>
					<li>Planned weekly marketing emails</li>
					<li>Sourced an external agency to begin work on SEO, and work towards paid advertising</li>
					<li>Currently planning photoshoots and content creation with our social media content creator to get a more consistent posting schedule up and running</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<img src="/muscle-rage-price-list.webp" alt="" class="img-border">
			<img src="/muscle-rage-lipodrol.webp" alt="" class="img-border">
			<img src="/muscle-rage-website.webp" alt="" class="img-border column-span">
			<div>
				<h4>
					Web Design
				</h4>
				<ul class="last-item">
					<li>Re-designed the website in Figma, before moving to build in WordPress with the Avada theme</li>
					<li>Carried out basic SEO, adding meta descriptions & titles, ensuring all product descriptions were present, and increased word count where needed</li>
					<li>Created 3D product renders of all products using Blender, and started updating old product images</li>
					<li>Hooked up a product feed plugin, & added products to google merchant center</li>
					<li>Set up GA4, Tag Manager, Meta Pixel, Search Console etc. to allow the brand to plan future marketing activity</li>
				</ul>
				<a href="https://musclerage.co.uk" class="btn">Check out the Website</a>
			</div>
		</section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
	.last-item {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
</style>